^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The club void is extremely powerful, and as you can see, the hand can be made. Taking the spade finesse was very reasonable. However once it loses, Ally should maximize her chances. After the second club, her only potential loser is a diamond. She may be able to set up hearts, so that is what she should try after playing the 2nd spade--(trick four spade). |
