NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Once that spade wins, and I show out she should play heart to the King and heart back to the Ace and ruff a heart, if the Q does not drop. If that does not work, she can always try the diamond finesse. That maximizes the chances. Elizabeth's 5C bid was excellent as well, BTW. She can count us for 10 trumps, and with no defense, at favorable vul, 5 clubs must be a good sacrifice. Although it does turn out I am down 4, taking only my 7 club tricks but I think the bid is a nice one.|
